        <content type="html">
            <![CDATA[
                    <p><img src="https://danielmarin.me/media/posts/22/Richmond-2.jpeg" class="type:primaryImage" alt="" /></p>
                
  <p>
    This is a documentary that I created at my final year at university where I wanted to highlight my video editing and recording skills, sound design and content creation abilities. The mini documentary talks about the healing properties of ambient music and relaxing sounds to improve our mental health. The video features research in the subject as well as original recordings from Richmond Park.&nbsp;
  </p>
